comments: Alvarado (NOP) briefly has his arms around James' (LAL) midsection before quickly disengaging.
Alvarado's (NOP) right arm comes forward prior to marginal contact occurring with James' (LAL) off-arm near the elbow.

Alvarado (NOP) collapses his left hand against James's (LAL) body and avoids initiating contact with James's arm when he reaches in.  Jones (NOP) lowers his arm and makes clean contact with the ball to steal the pass.
Reaves (LAL) and Alvarado (NOP) come together in the air after Alvarado releases the pass and incidental body contact occurs.
Jones (NOP) firms up in a defensive position in Reaves' (LAL) path as he releases the pass and marginal contact occurs as Reaves moves around him to slip the contact.
Davis (LAL) and Reaves (LAL) are each moving forward when marginal body contact occurs with McCollum (NOP) as McCollum is returning to the floor following the release of the pass.
Russell (LAL) initiates contact across Nance Jr.'s (NOP) left arm during his upward shooting motion and affects the layup attempt.
Jones (NOP) and James (LAL) briefly engage and disengage with one another, and marginal contact occurs along the perimeter.
Daniels (NOP) brushes Reaves' (LAL) left arm and marginal contact occurs as Reaves passes at the end of the drive.
Murphy III (NOP) is turning away from Vincent (LAL) and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.
Jones (NOP) makes intentional foot-to-ball contact during the inbound.
Jones (NOP) and Daniels (NOP) each legally contest James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) and Nance Jr. (NOP) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound.
Nance Jr. (NOP) steps forward into Davis's (LAL) lower body and initiates contact that affects his layup attempt.
Vincent (LAL) slides alongside of McCollum (NOP) on the perimeter and the contact is marginal.
McCollum (NOP) commits a take foul on Reaves (LAL).
Nance Jr. (NOP) establishes himself in Vincent's (LAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact as Vincent moves into him when the pick is set in transition.
McCollum (NOP) wraps Davis's (LAL) midsection and initiates further contact with Davis' right arm as he receives the inbound.
Vincent (LAL) legally contests McCollum's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
